data.meta_description:
35 likes, 1 comments - hollersandhills on June 25, 2024: "Episode 1 is here! 

Exploring Dolly Parton’s hometown of Sevierville has never been more convenient. From walks Downtown with the county historian to an intimate Chef’s Table experience at The Appalachian, this episode takes you on a journey. 

Listen on Apple or Spotify, and watch on Youtube!

Also, check out hollersandhillspod.com (linked in our bio) for information on the podcast, future episodes, and more!".
